@cyrielleverstuyft  Finding the perfect balance between earthy tones and a Midas touch. 🕊️ There’s something undeniably magnetic about the way this olive drape meets the iconic gold Bottega Veneta Pouch. It’s sophisticated, it’s effortless, and it’s just the right amount of bold—exactly how we like it. ✨

